Familial Isolated Pituitary Adenome (FIPA, incl. Familial Isolated Somatotropinomas, FIS, IFS, Familial Acromegaly) gene: AIP
Li-Fraumeni Syndrome (LFS, SBLA syndrome (Sarcoma Breast Leukemia Adrenal cancer), incl.: Cancer with In Vitro Radioresistence, Familial, Li-Fraumeni-like s.) gene: BRCA2, TP53
Familial Acute Myeloid Leukemia (AML) gene: CEBPA
Familial Clustering of Chronic Lymphocytic Leukemia (CLL) gene: DAPK1
Familial Pheochromocytoma (Adrenal) gene: MAX, TMEM127, VHL
Aicardi Syndrome gene: AIC#
Bloom Syndrome gene: BLM
Carney Complex (Carney syndrome, NAME syndrome, LAMB syndrome, Familial Myxoma syndrome) gene: CNC2#, PRKAR1A
Familial Clustering of Chordoma gene: T/TFT
Costello Syndrome (incl.: Facio-Cutaneous-Skeletal syndrome) gene: HRAS
Cowden Syndrome (CS, Cowden disease, Multiple Hamartoma Syndrome, incl.: Lhermitte-Duclos; part of PTEN hamartoma tumour syndrome (PHTS) / PTEN-MATCHS, Cowden-like syndrome) gene: ATK1, KILLIN, PIK3CA, PTEN, SDHB, SDHD
Denys-Drash Syndrome (Early Onset Nephrotic Syndrome-WT1 associated) gene: WT1
Hereditary Desmoid Disease (Familial Infiltrative Mesenteric Fibromatosis) gene: APC
Diamond-Blackfan Anemia (DBA, Congenital Hypoplastic Anemia, Blackfan-Diamond Anemia, incl.: Aase syndrome) gene: RPS19
Congenital Dyskeratosis (Zinsser-Engman-Cole syndrome, Dyskeratosis Congenita) gene: DKC1, TERC, TERT, TINF2
Ollier disease / Maffuci syndrome (Osteochondromatosis, Enchondromatosis) gene: IDH1, IDH2, PTHR1
Frasier Syndrome gene: WT1
Familial Adenomatous Polyposis (FAP, incl.: Gardner s., Attenuated FAP, Flat Adenoma s., Oldfield s.) gene: APC
Noonan Syndrome (Male Turner syndrome, Pterygium Colli syndrome, incl. Noonan-like/Multiple Giant Cell Lesion syndrome; Noonan s. with multiple lentigines/LEOPARD syndrome) gene: CBL, KRAS, NRAS, PTPN11, RAF1, SOS1
McCune-Albright Syndrome (Polyostotic Fibrous Dysplasia; MAS) gene: GNAS1
